name: Mystic Barrage

When in Overcharge, ATK is increased by 35622 for 15 sec and each auto attack reduces skill cooldown by 10%. All effects cannot be dispelled, and Charge will not stack during Overcharge state

name: Celestial Arrow
description: Deals 193398 M.DMG to 3 enemies and push them back, leaving a Judgment Sigil on them for 15 sec. Deals additional ??? M.DMG to Non-Hero enemies and causes them to take 25% increased M.DMG for 10 sec

name: Purifying Blaze
description: Deals 382266 M.DMG to frontal enemies in a straight line. Deals additional 729969 M.DMG that ignores DEF to targets with Judgment Sigil, and reduces their Heal Rate by 50% for 10 sec

description: Deals 541319 M.DMG to the target and enemies in a nearby range. Enemies with Judgment Sigil take 50% increased M.DMG and become silenced for 5 sec. Afterward, grants immunity to M.DMG to all allies for 5 sec

Once during every battle, upon reaching near death HP, deals 330835 M.DMG to enemies inflicted by Judgement Sigils and stuns them for 3 sec, while casting a shield that blocks 563411 DMG to all allies for 5 sec. Gains immunity to CC while the shield is in effect. When the shield effect takes place, consumes all mana, and all skill cooldown is increased by 50%

name: Pillar of Light

name: Critical Intensity
description: Deals 359697 M.DMG to frontal enemies in a straight line. This attack's Crit DMG is increased by 100%

name: Light's Judgment
description: Attacks all enemies 3 times, dealing a total of 545880 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 5 sec. If the target is not a Hero, each hit deals 124305 additional M.DMG. Killing an enemy with this Skill reduces Cooldown by 30%.

name: Blessing of Light

Blessing of Light can be stacked up to max 10 times. Each stack increases own ATK by 5222, DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies by 7%, and reduces DMG taken from Non-Hero enemies by 3%.

name: Sword of the Sun
description: Deals 138175 M.DMG to enemy and surrounding enemies within range, and inflicts Stun for 3 sec

name: Blessing of the Sun
description: Imbues the Blessing of the Sun to the ally with the highest ATK, reducing cooldown of all skills by 20% and increasing ATK by 38948 for 15 sec

After the end of the casting, heals HP of allies within range, excluding self, by 153676, and deals 119552 M.DMG on enemies, and knocks them down for 3 sec

name: Curse of the Sun
description: Upon attack, inflicts Curse of the Sun on the target for 10 sec. Enemies with 10 stacks of Curses of the Sun will consume the stack to receive 111223 M.DMG, and become inflicted with Blind for 2 sec, having their ATK reduced by 20% for 10 sec

name: Holy Nova
description: Targets the ally with the lowest HP and allies nearby to heal 194058 HP. Deals 64342 M.DMG to enemies near the target, and reduces enemy ATK Spd by 25% for 10 sec.

name: Spear of Light
description: Deals 185571 M.DMG, inflicts knockback, and shackles the target enemy for 6 sec. Enemies inflicted by shackle take 25% increased M.DMG while the effect lasts.

name: Holy Sanctuary
description: Grants Invincibility to all allies for 7 sec and heals 298431 HP for the duration of skill.

name: Training of God

name: Circle of Futility
description: Attacks the target and nearby enemies within range, dealing 207231 M.DMG and placing the Circle of Futility. Circle of Futility deals 367856 M.DMG, reduces ATK Spd by 300 , and prevents enemies from receiving positive effects over 4 sec. A 4 sec Cooldown will be applied at the beginning of the first battle.

name: Battle Initiation
description: Attacks enemies within frontal range, dealing 249599 M.DMG and knocking them back. Then, increases own All DMG Reduction by 200 and DEF by 26118, and gains immunity to CC for 15 sec. A 8 sec Cooldown will be applied at the beginning of the first battle.

name: Destroyer
description: Deals 429520 M.DMG over 10 attacks to nearby enemies in a circular range around self. Then, attacks enemies in a wide surrounding area, dealing 376852 M.DMG and stunning them for 5 sec. If the target is not a Hero, each attack will deal additional 42074 M.DMG. A 10 sec Cooldown will be applied at the beginning of the first battle.

name: Breakdown
description: Bernheim cannot recover Mana, and all his Skills do not consume any Mana. Normal and Skill attacks inflict Breakdown to enemies for 10 sec, reducing their Heal Rate by 1%, and increasing own ATK by 3085 and Heal Rate by 0.5%. All effects stack up to 50 times.

name: Tremble!

After 3.5 seconds, Cain dispels negative effects from the target and the allies nearby. Afterwards, heals their HP by 237423. [The God King’s Blessing] is irremovable.

name: Kneel.
description: Cain deals 212620 P.DMG to the enemy with the highest ATK and casts [Sealing Technique of the Tyrant] that reduces the target's ATK Spd 350 and prevents the target from receiving any positive effects for 5 sec. After 5 sec, Cain deals 176824 P.DMG to the target and the enemies nearby, inflicting stun for 3 sec. [Sealing Technique of the Tyrant] is irremovable.

name: Behold My Might.
description: Cain turns into a [Tyrant] and constantly attacks the target, dealing 82084 P.DMG with each hit. While Cain is in [Tyrant] form, [Tremble!] and [Gaze Upon My Almighty Power!] change to [Kneel.] and [Now Die.]. Upon using the Skill again, he returns to [God King] form. [The God King’s Mercy] - While Cain is in God King form, reduces DMG all allies take 10%. [Dignity of the Tyrant] – While Cain is in Tyrant form, increases DMG all enemies take 10%.

name: Gaze Upon My Almighty Power!
description: Increases All DEF of allies nearby self by 5222 for 10 sec 10 times. DEF Boost effect stacks up to 10 time(s), and if this Skill is cast on an ally with 10 stacks, increases the target’s ATK 150088 and grants immunity to CC for 10 sec.

name: Now Die

name: I Am the King of the Desert.
description: At the beginning of each battle, gains an irremoveable stack of [King of the Desert]. Each Stack of of [King of the Desert] increases the effect of [The God King's Mercy] and [Dignity of the Tyrant] by 5%. Additionally, recovers 100 Mana every second, and increases ATK by 13055. If [King of the Desert] is stacked 3 time(s) or more, self deals 50% increased DMG to Bosses. [King of the Desert] can be stacked up to 5 times.

name: Softly~
description: Heals all allies by 231308 HP and deals 161713 M.DMG to all enemies. Hit enemies are inflicted by Silence for 2 sec.

name: Fiercely!
description: For 15 sec, all allies' ATK is increased by 11874 and Crit Chance is increased by 700.

name: Tempting Wave
description: Deals 322459 M.DMG to an enemy with the highest ATK. If this skill is used in Arena, inflicts Charm on the target for 7 sec. If this skill is used outside the Arena, enemy takes 25% increased M.DMG. Charmed enemies cannot use any skills, and deals auto attack to own allies.

name: Gentle Touch
description: At the start of each battle, reduces mana cost by 2 orbs for a single skill, and all allies' DEF is increased by 20181 for 5 sec.

name: Outta the way!
description: Marks the farthest enemy as the [Villain], reducing its ATK Spd by 200 for 15 sec. Then, moves to the target to deal 130933 P.DMG. After using this Skill, [Crushing Kick!] becomes available.

name: Crushing Kick!
description: Attacks the target, dealing 155307 P.DMG and knocking it away for 4 sec. Enemies marked as [Villain] are prioritized. After using this Skill, [Tempest Kick!] becomes available.

name: Tempest Kick!
description: Moves to the farthest enemy, dealing 185279 P.DMG and stunning it for 4 sec. Enemies marked as [Villain] are prioritized.

name: Infinite Potential
description: Deals 177450 P.DMG to nearby enemies in a circular range of self, knocking them down for 3 sec. While under [Infinite Potential], Normal and Skill attacks deal 29568 P.DMG to Heroes and 88713 P.DMG to Non-Hero enemies. This effect is irremovable.

name: WA-TAAAAAH!!!
description: Deals 495594 P.DMG over 6 attacks to nearby enemies in a circular range of self. Afterward, deals 246321 P.DMG to the target and its nearby enemies, knocking them down for 4 sec. While under [Infinite Potential], [Special Move. Meteor Kick!!!] becomes available for 10 sec.

name: Special Move. Meteor Kick!!!
description: Launches a full force attack that deals 762136 P.DMG to the target and enemies nearby, stunning them for 5 sec. This Skill will always be a Critical Hit.

name: Inborn Talent
description: Increases own DEF by 4981 and Crit Chance by 200. Cecilia's Normal and Skill attacks will not miss.

name: I'll Break You!
description: Prevents the target from receiving positive effects for 4 seconds, and attacks to inflict 193762 P.DMG and knocks the target back. Inflicts 74425 P.DMG after 1 second to enemies around the target and stuns them for 4 seconds.

name: Remove Limit

While [Remove Limit] is activated, consumes 1.5% of current HP every 1 second, gains Immunity to CC, and increases Crit DMG by 50% and ATK Spd by 500, and enhances normal attacks. The HP consumption, Crit DMG and ATK Spd Boost grow stronger over time. This effect is irremovable, and is automatically deactivated when HP falls under 25% or below.

name: Burn, Spear of Fury
description: Charges at an enemy, dealing 130278 P.DMG and knocking it down. Affterward and explodes the ground around self to attack 4 times, dealing a total of 256944 P.DMG and inflicting Stun for 5 sec. Each hit recovers HP equal to 3% of Chase's Max HP + 25% of DMG.

name: Remember This in Hell
description: Chase is not affected by Lifesteal stats. Instead, increases self's Max HP by 20%, Crit Chance by 100, CC ACC by 100, and ACC by 100. Whenever HP drops by 1%, increaes Crit DMG 1% and ATK Spd by 4. Upon taking a fatal DMG by 40%, ATK Spd 400, and gaining immunity to CC for the duration. The resurrection effect can be activated only once in battle, and resurrected Chase cannot use skills.

name: Light of Annihilation
description: Deals 276148 M.DMG that ignores DEF to the target, and inflicts stun for 3 sec. Deals additional 199099 M.DMG that ignores DEF to Non-Hero targets. After use, removes all stacked Lights and gains irremovable Red Light.

name: Enemy Blockade
description: Dispels all negative effects from self, deals 70196 M.DMG to all enemies, and silences them for 1 sec. After use, removes all stacked Lights and gains irremovable Blue Light.

name: Green Zone

Enemies in the Green Zone cannot receive positive effects and takes a total of 160980 M.DMG over 3 sec, having their Heal Rate reduced by 30%. After use, removes all stacked Lights and gains irremovable Green Light.

Red Light - Increases DMG of normal attack by 100%, and upon attack, reduces Cooldown of [Light of Annihilation] by 1 sec. Blue Light - Reduces DMG of normal attack by 50%, but deals DMG to the entire enemy. Targets take 30% increased M.DMG for 10 sec. Green Light - Reduces DMG of normal attack by 20%, but deals DMG to 2 enemies. Heal Rate of the target is reduced by 20% for 5 sec.

name: Cut Ground

name: Shield Strike
description: Deals 153118 P.DMG proportional to Clause's P.DEF to enemies in range and knocks them back. Hit enemies have their All DEF and ATK Spd reduced by 30% and 500 for 200 sec, respectively. When Clause succesfully blocks an attack, reduces this Skill's Cooldown by 0.5 sec.

name: Guardian Shield
description: Increases all allies' P.DEF by 18044, P.Crit Resistance is increased by 300, and reduces P.DMG they take by 25% for 20 sec.

When an ally excluding self takes DMG, increases all allies' P.DEF by 20% and P.Crit Resistance by 200 for 5 sec. This effect only activates once every 10 sec.

name: Fire Ball

name: Target will be Eliminated.

Depending on the focusing time, the effect's range increases, and DMG is increased up to max 100%. Once the focus is completed, knocks back the enemy far away.

name: Judgment Upon Them!

description: Attacks a random enemy 5 times, dealing 734270 M.DMG in total. If the target is not a Hero, deals additional 230620 M.DMG. While [Grant Me Strength!] is active, an enemy with highest ATK will be prioritized.

[Dark Lord] Additionally attacks enemies in wide range 1 time, dealing 210711 P.DMG and knocking them down for 3 sec. Requires 5 or more stacks of [Dark Energy] for use.

name: Doom

[Dark Lord] Deals 192720 P.DMG to 1 enemy furthest away and pulls it in front of self, exploding Darkness afterward. Requires 15 or more stacks of [Dark Energy] for use.

Upon use, consume all stacks to increase own ATK by 2000 and DEF Penetration by 10 per stack.

Normal attacks grant [Dark Energy] stacks. [Dark Energy] can be stacked up to max 40 times and is irremovable.

name: Penetration

name: Will to Win

name: Steel Fortress
description: Upon DMG block during casting, jump attack DMG is increased by 7%. Also, deals 49076 P.DMG to enemy and inflicts stun. After casting, jumps and attacks the enemy, dealing 181181 P.DMG and stunning them for 4 sec. Gains immunity to CC while the skill is in use.

name: Spearhead
description: All allies' P.DEF is increased by 7118 and P.Block chance is increased by 250.

name: Dark Rampage
description: Deals 535290 M.DMG to an enemy.

name: Black Shackle
description: Deals 333668 M.DMG to enemies in range and shackles them for 6 sec.

name: Shadow Wave
description: Deals 393125 M.DMG to enemies in a straight line and inflicts Blind for 6 sec.

name: Black Stain
description: Each auto attack deals extra 41573 M.DMG that ignores target's M.DEF.

name: This Will Hurt!
description: After increasing CC Resist of allies within self's range by 200 for 10 sec, attacks enemies to deal 268437 M.DMG and causes them to take 30% increased M.DMG for 10 sec. Hit enemies become unable to recover Mana for 3 sec.

name: On Guard!
description: Dispels negative effects from all allies and increases P.DEF by 15674 + 4% of Dosarta's ATK for 10 sec.

name: Hya! Kya! Take this!
description: Attacks a target 4 times, dealing a total of 868500 M.DMG and stunning it for 4 sec. Afterward, launches a final attack on frontal enemies within range, dealing 293159 M.DMG and pulling them to the center. Against Non-Hero enemies, each attack deals additional 150072 M.DMG that ignores DEF.

name: Let Us Challenge Together!
description: Upon blocking, reduces Cooldown of self's active Skills by 1 sec and increases P.DEF of self by 8781 + 1% of Dosarta's ATK for 4 sec. A 6 -sec Cooldown will be applied.

name: Absorbing Blow
description: Deals 330336 M.DMG that ignores enemy DEF, and heals 25% of DMG as HP.

name: Nightmare
description: Moves behind the furthest enemy and deals 183572 M.DMG. Hit enemies take 30% increased M.DMG for 10 sec.

name: Devil's Prom
description: Deals 695356 M.DMG to all enemies in range. Gains CC immunity while using this skill.

name: Harvest
description: When an enemy is killed by this hero, ATK is increased by 16381 for 12 sec, and all skill cooldown is reduced by 30%.

name: Sweet Blood
description: Deals 117655 P.DMG to all enemies and Lifesteals HP equal to 10% of DMG dealt. Each hit reduces Cooldown of [Sweet Blood] by 0.5 sec and grants 1 irremovable stack of [Sweet Blood]. [Sweet Blood] can be stacked up to max 5 times, and using the Skill with 5 stacks of [Sweet Blood] grants 1 additional hit and removes [Sweet Blood] stacks.

name: Soaking Blood
description: Dispels all negative effects and gains immunity to all CCs, P.DMG, and M.DMG for 5 sec. Inflicts 1 stack of [Soaking Blood] on all enemies, and additional 1 stack upon attacking a target with [Soaking Blood]. [Soaking Blood] can be stacked up to 6 times. For every 3 stack(s) of [Soaking Blood], hit count increases by 1 and removes [Soaking Blood] stacks upon attacking.

name: Blood Liberation

name: Life Drinker
description: Increases ATK by 4748 and Max HP by 23748 upon killing an enemy. Stacks up to max 50. Upon taking fatal DMG, casts [Soaking Blood], and decreases Max HP by 40%. This effect is not applied when [Soaking Blood] is in cooldown. This skill consumes all Mana upon activation.

name: This Is My Game
description: Attacks a random enemy 3 times, dealing 122090 M.DMG and stunning it for 3 sec. If the 3 attacks land on the same enemy, deals additional 256654 M.DMG that ignores DEF.

name: My Turn
description: Rolls the dice and increases ATK and Crit DMG of 2 random allies by 4748 and 7% respectively for 60 sec. This effect can be stacked up to max 10 times, and the number of targets increases by 1 per 1 pip on the rolled dice.

name: Shall I Try My Luck?
description: Attacks all enemies and deals 377720 M.DMG, permanently reducing Cooldown of this skill by 2 sec or increasing its DMG by 30%, each with a 50% chance. This effect can be stacked up to max 10 times.

name: This Is Not a Trick
description: Every 10 sec, increases own ATK by 4274 and DEF by 2611. This effect can be stacked up to max 10 times.

name: Purification of Life
description: Heals HP of all allies by 10122 and increases Heal Rate of healed allies by 25% for 15 sec.

name: Uproar of Naav Gehen
description: Deals 103357 P.DMG to all enemies and increases P.DMG the hit enemies take by 25% for 10 sec.

name: Magic Circle of Life
description: Places a magic circle in a wide range of self for 12 sec, healing HP of all allies within range by 42890 every sec and increasing their ATK Spd by 500.

name: Naav Gehen of Gluttony
description: Deals 51983 P.DMG to the enemy and enemies within a wide range of the target, dispelling positiv effects from hit enemies and places a magic circle for 12 sec. The magic circle deals 48431 P.DMG to enemies within range and reduces ATK by 20% every sec.

name: Origin of Life
description: Creates a shield that absorbs 318005 DMG and recovers 100 mana every sec for 15 sec on all allies. For the duration of the Shield, gains immmunity to CC.

name: Rampage of Naav Gehen
description: Deals a total of 333474 P.DMG over 6 times to enemies within a wide range of the target and inflicts Stun for 2 sec. The last hit deals 166993 P.DMG and inflicts Stun for 5 sec.

name: Alchemy of Green

[Alchemist of the Green Evan] Purification of Life, Magic Circle of Life, and Origin of Life become available for use. After Skill use, Evan turns into 'Alchemist of the Dark Evan.' [Alchemist of the Dark Evan] Uproar of Naav Gehen, Naav Gehen of Gluttony, and Rampage of Naav Gehen become available for use. After skill use, Evan turns into 'Alchemist of the Green Evan.'

name: Destructive Instinct
description: Swipes nearby enemies in a circular range and deals 146299 M.DMG. Then strikes the ground, dealing 190017 M.DMG and knocking down enemies for 3 sec. [Fury] - Consumes 15% of current HP to activate. Effect range increases and swipe attack draws in enemies.

name: Dawning Despair
description: Dashes to an enemy with the highest ATK and deals 304072 M.DMG to enemies in range, reducing their ATK Spd by 300. [Fury] - Consumes 10% of current HP to activate. Effect range increases, Stuns target for 3 sec, and increases own ATK Spd by 300 for 10 sec.

name: Strike of Doom
description: Charges energy and attacks the enemy, dealing 331722 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 3 sec. This DMG ignores the target's DMG Reduction effect. [Fury] - Consumes 20% of current HP to activate. Attacks enemies in range of target and DMG is tripled.

name: Cursed Blood
description: Ezekiel gains 1 stack of 'Cursed Blood' at the end of Skill. At 3 stacks, consumes Cursed Blood to reset Cooldown of all Skills, dealing 247808 M.DMG to nearby enemies, knocking them down for 3 sec, and activating Fury for 10 sec. Fury is irremovable. While in Fury state, Ezekiel goes into auto-battle mdoe that cannot be controlled, increasing ATK by 126581, DMG of normal attacks by x2, and enhancing all Skill effects. During Fury state, Skill use does not grant a stack of Cursed Blood, but killing an enemy will grant a stack.

name: Light of Doom
description: Heals HP of the ally with the lowest HP and nearby allies by 402686 and increases Heal Rate by 20% for 10 sec. Afterward, explodes the area around the target and deals 194058 M.DMG to enemies in range, reducing their Heal Rate by 20% for sec. If this Skill is used with 1 or more stacks of [Darkened Power], consumes 1 stack and dispels positive effects of all enemies within range.

name: Blessing of Doom
description: Grants [Blessing of Doom] to 4 allies with the lowest HP, absorbing 428716 DMG for 10 sec. The shield grants immunity to CC and increases ATK Spd by 500 for the duration. If this Skill is used with 1 or more stacks of [Darkened Power], consumes 1 stack to dispel negative effects from self and additionally dispels negative effects from targets.

name: Heaven's Vengeance
description: Brings Heaven's Vengeance upon a random enemy and nearby enemies over 20 hits, dealing 67184 M.DMG each hit and increases All DMG the target takes by 10% for 20 sec. 500 additional DEF Penetration applies to this Skill. If this skill is used with 1 or more stacks of [Darkened Power], consumes 1 stack and inflicts Stun on the hit enemies for 0.5 sec each hit. The DMG Boost effect can be stacked up to max 5 times.

name: Tainted Angel
description: As Fallen Frey has been corrupted by the darkness, she takes 15% increased DMG, but she recovers 400 Mana every sec, and when her Mana is at 100%, she gains [Darkened Power] every sec. [Darkened Power] can be stacked up to max 2 times and is irremovable.

name: Tempest Blade
description: Attacks the target and the enemies near it 3 times, dealing a total of 320892 P.DMG. If the target is not a Hero, inflicts a total of 445640 additional P.DMG over 5 sec.

name: Flashstep
description: Moves to the enemy with the highest ATK, dispels positive effects from the target, inflicts Silence for 2 sec, and leaves a Mark for 10 sec. Afterwar, Fluss' all attacks prioritize the Marked target and deal 20598 P.DMG per attack. When the Marked target dies, resets Cooldown of this Skill and recovers 2000 Mana.

name: Bloody Petals
description: Deals a total of 742653 P.DMG to an enemy over 16 hits, and suppresses the target while casting. This DMG ignores the target's Block effects.

name: Spell Cutter
description: Increases own M.DEF by 11874. Upon taking M.DMG, deals 118767 P.DMG to the attacker, reduces its ATK by 30% for 5 sec, and dodges All M.DMG for 3 sec. This effect activates only once every 10 sec.

name: Miraculous Light
description: Dispels negative effects from the ally with the lowest HP, healing HP of the target by 607131 and HP of allies nearby equal to 40% of Heal Rate.

name: Blessings of Light
description: Casts a shield that absorbs 318005 DMG for 12 sec on all allies. While the shield is active, the target increases its ATK by 20%, Heal Rate by 50%, and gains immunity to CC.

name: Heaven's Vengeance
description: Attacks the target and its nearby enemies 6 times, dealing up to 67756 M.DMG. 500 additional Crit Chance applies to this Skill. Hit targets are blinded for 6 sec and take 25% increased All DMG for 10 sec.

name: Goddess Grace
description: Reduces All DMG taken by 15%. At the beginning of each battle, and every 15 sec, increases M.DEF of 1 ally with the lowest HP by 10918 for 10 sec and heals HP of the target by 15% for the duration on Skill.

name: Smash
description: Deals 230826 P.DMG to enemies within range, and the first attack knocks them down for 3 sec and reduces DEF Penetration by 250 for 10 sec.

name: Battle Roar
description: Dispels negative effects from all allies, increases their ATK by 49866, ATK Spd by 300, and P.DEF by 16622 for 15 sec.

name: Vortex
description: Charges to the front, dealing 606876 P.DMG over 12 times to nearby enemies within circular range of self and draws them in during casting. While using this Skill, gains immunity to CC, and the last attack freezes the enemy for 4 sec.

name: Enrage
description: Increases own ATK by 3792, CC Resist by 30, and DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies by 1.5% every sec. This effect can be stacked up to max 20 times. At 20 stacks or more, increases DMG of normal attacks by 100%.

name: Quick Strikes
description: Strikes the target 7 times, dealing a total of 522900 P.DMG. The last hit increases the target's P.DMG taken by 25% for 10 sec.

name: Advent of the War God
description: Dispel all negative effects on self and deal 235546 P.DMG to nearby enemies within a small radius, gaining the Status 'War God' for 10 sec. While in War God mode, ATK is boosted by 36329 and all auto attacks have a 30% chance to consume 5% mana to deal an extra attack of 129987 extra P.DMG. Upon taking M.DMG, dodge all M.DMG for 1 sec. Dodge effect only activates 1 time in every 2 sec.

name: Ultimate Punch!
description: Charges energy and sprints toward frontal enemies, dealing 544060 P.DMG to enemies in range and inflicting stun for 3 sec. If the target is a boss, attack ignores target DEF.

name: This will hurt!
description: Upon hitting a single target with 5 auto attacks, deals 65548 extra DMG that ignores DEF.

name: That Is It
description: Deals a total of 118440 P.DMG over 7 attacks to frontal enemies. Each attack increases P.DMG the enemies take by 4% for 10 sec. This effect stacks up to max 7 times. Deals additional 256249 P.DMG to Non-Hero target.

name: I Will Not Stay My Hand
description: Deals 278980 P.DMG over 10 attacks to nearby enemies in a circular range of self and stuns them for 1 sec. The final attack deals 87473 P.DMG to frontal enemies and stuns them for 3 sec.

name: Time For Counterattack
description: Calling upon the strength of the Imperial Shield, deals 269079 P.DMG to nearby enemies in a large circular range of self and knocks them down for 3 sec. Dispels negative effects from all allies, increases ATK by 22559 for 20 sec, and increases DEF by 10211.

name: Pride of Imperial Knights
description: Increases ATK of all allies by 8307. At the beginning of each battle, increases DMG to Non-Hero enemies by 10% for 20 sec, reducing DMG received by 10%.

name: I See Through Your Every Move!
description: Throws a grenade, and fires a submachine gun, dealing 235543 P.DMG to the target and the enemies nearby. Hanus gains 20 Ammo afterward. Hit enemies take 25% increased P.DMG for 10 sec, and are blinded for 4 sec. Ammo can be stacked up to max 300 times.

name: Shoot You Full of Holes!
description: Shoots a machine gun 10 times to frontal enemies in a wide area, dealing a total of 194520 P.DMG. Afterwards, if Hanus is possessing Ammo, she consumes 2 Ammo per shot to attack enemies until she runs out of Ammo. While in this state, Hanus takes 25% additional DMG. Every 1 st shot increases DMG of this Skill by 8%. The DMG Boost effect can be stacked up to max 50 times.

name: Hide If You Can!
description: Fires a mortar at a frontal area, dealing 363918 P.DMG in a wide area. Hanus gains 50 Ammo afterwards. Hit enemies are stunned for 5 sec. This Skill ignores target's P.Block and M.Block.

name: I Shall Train You Hard!
description: Hanus is not affected by ATK Spd effects, and increases ATK of all allies by 17811 + 5% of Hanus' ATK. If activated during Guild battles, this effect is amplified by 2 times. [Guild Battle] - Guild Raid, Guild Conquest, Guild War

name: Funeral Rites
description: Deals 140671 M.DMG to enemies in range, stunning them for 5 sec.

name: Mark of Death
description: Engraves a Mark on all enemies for 30 sec and deals 105060 continuous M.DMG. Enemies engraved with Mark takes 25% increased M.DMG. This effect increases by 20% upon every use. This effect can be stacked up to max 5 times and is irremovable.

name: Day of Ruin
description: Increase M.DEF of all allies by 10685. Upon taking fatal DMG, enters a coffin for 5 sec and heals HP equal to 463206 + 6% of Max HP. While inside the coffin, Jane is not affcted by ATK Spd effects, ignores All DMG, and deals M.DMG equal to 5% of Max HP to nearby enemies every sec.

name: Rest in Peace
description: Upon taking a deathblow, enters a coffin for 5 sec and heals 463206 + 6% of Max HP. Gains immunity to all DMG while inside the coffin.

name: Best Dish
description: Removes negative effects from all allies, heals a total of 461902 HP over 7 second(s), and increases DEF by 9022. When there are 2 stacks or more [Excellent Ingredient], consumes 2 stacks to double the DEF Boost.

name: Juno's Spicy Special
description: Removes positive effects from all enemies, deals a total of 764220 P.DMG over 10 second(s), and enemies take 20% increased P.DMG. When there are 2 stacks or more [Excellent Ingredient], consumes 2 stacks to double the P.DMG that enemies take.

name: Power-up
description: Casts a shield on the ally with the lowest HP that absorbs 672692 DMG and grants Immunity to CC along with 1 orb of Mana. When there are 2 stacks or more [Excellent Ingredient], consumes 2 stacks to double the Mana Recovery.

name: Help Yourself, Then Get Lost!
description: Attacks the target and nearby enemies around it, dealing 278279 P.DMG and reducing their Mana by 1 orb. If the target is not a Hero, inflicts 367178 additional P.DMG that ignores DEF. When there are 2 stacks or more [Excellent Ingredient], consumes 2 stacks to double the Mana Reduction.

name: Cook from Hell
description: Removes all negative effects from self, heals 81783 HP, and transforms into a Cook from Hell. [Best Dish] and [Power-up] are changed to [Juno's Spicy Special] and [Help Yourself, Then Get Lost!] respectively. Gains 1 stack of irremovable [Excellent Ingredient]. When the skill is used again, transforms into a Cook from Heaven.

name: Open for Business!
description: While transformed into a Cook from Heaven, increases DEF of all allies by 6644 and their heal rate by 15%. While transformed into a Cook from Hell, reduces DEF of all enemies by 10% and their heal rate by 20%.

name: Anti-personnel Laser
description: Attacks the target 4 times, dealing a total of 302976 M.DMG and inflicting knockback. Attacks all enemies with the last blow, dealing 151496 M.DMG and blowing them away for 3 seconds.

name: Siege Laser
description: Attacks the target inflicting 483353 M.DMG. Crit DMG is applied 200% higher.

name: Wide-area Cannon
description: Attacks a random target and nearby enemies in range 4 times, inflicting a total of 345276 M.DMG and stunning them for 4 seconds.

name: Focused Fire
description: Attacks a random target 15 times, inflicting a total of 331920 M.DMG, and inflicts Focused Fire for 20 seconds. Inflicts 737 extra M.DMG with each stack of Focused Fire on the enemy. Focused Fire can be stacked up to 30 times.

name: Release Siege Weapon
description: Kara turns into Siege Weapon mode and attacks the enemy, inflicting 35517 M.DMG with each hit. When in Siege Weapon mode, changes Anti-personnel Laser and Wide-area Cannon skills to Siege Laser and Focused Fire skills. When the skill is used again, returns to Anti-personnel Weapon mode.

name: Essence of Technomagic
description: While in [Anti-personnel Weapon] mode, increases All DEF by 28729, and while in [Siege Weapon] mode, increases DMG against bosses by 25%, takes 30% increased DMG from enemies, and gains immunity to CC. Dealing DMG to an enemy recovers 70 Mana each hit.

name: Judgment Blade
description:
Attacks frontal enemies in a circular range of self 2 times, dealing 202500 P.DMG and knocks them down for 2.5 sec.
[Proxy of God] Attacks enemies in a wider range to deal 253264 P.DMG and knock them down for 3.5 sec.

name: Valiant Dash
description:
Attacks the target 3 times, charging behind it to deal 265089 P.DMG and increase P.DMG it takes by 25% for 10 sec.
[Proxy of God] Attacks the target 3 times, charging behind it to deal 331182 P.DMG and increase P.DMG it takes by 25% for 10 sec, 500 additional Crit Chance applies to this Skill.

name: Proxy of God
description: Deals 75830 P.DMG to nearby enemies and inflicts Stun for 3 sec. Additionally, increases self's ATK by 52244, ATK Spd by 250, All Dodge Chance by 250, and DMG of normal attacks by 125% for 20 sec. Gains immunity to CC for the duration. This effect is irremovable.

name: Goddess Strike
description: Increases own All DEF by 15433 and All Dodge Chance by 200. When equipped with The Holy Sword, Aea, receives the blessing of the goddess that increases DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies by 30% and reduces DMG taken from Non-Hero enemies by 30%.

name: Thunderbolt
description: Attacks a random enemy 5 times, dealing 284155 M.DMG each hit and inflicting Electric Shock. If the target is already inflicted with Electric Shock, inflicts Stun for 3 sec.

name: Healing Rain
description: Heals 734550 HP of all allies over 5 times. For the duration of Skill, Kaulah gains immunity to CC and takes 50% reduced All DMG.

name: Swift Wind
description: For 15 sec, increases all allies' ATK by 40844, ATK Spd by 350, and Crit Chance by 350.

name: Chain Lightning
description: Deals 66669 M.DMG to 4 enemies every 15 sec, inflicts Electric Shock for 20 sec, and stuns them for 1 sec upon a Critical Hit. Enemies under Electric Shock take a total of 116080 M.DMG over 20 sec. For every enemy under Electric Shock, Kaulah takes 15% reduced DMG. This effect can be stacked up to max 3 times and is irremovable.

name: Mm, You Better Pay Attention!
description: Attacks an enemy 11 times, dealing a total of 143787 M.DMG. Afterward, summons a [Dark Whirlpool] for 4 sec that attack the target and nearby enemies 8 times, dealing a total of 166384 M.DMG. If Nocturnal Demonic Sword, [Night Sky] is selected, DMG of self's normal attacks increases by 50% and each normal attack reduces Cooldown of this Skill by 0.5 sec.

name: Heh, Let's Have Some Fun!
description: Dispels all negative effects from self and turns into [Show Dominion] state for 5 sec. While in [Shadow Dominion] state, ATK is increased by 75992 and HP does not fall below 10%. After Skill use, [Ha! Full of Openings!] can be used within 5 sec. If Umbral Demonic Sword, [Dark Shadow] is selected, the Mana Cost of this Skill is reduced by 1.

name: Ha! Full of Openings
description: Moves to the back of the enemy with the highest ATK, marking the target with [Dark Corrosion] and reducing the ATK Spd of the marked target by 400 for 10 sec. Kibera's attacks will prioritize the marked target. If [Umbral Demonic Sword, Dark Shadow] is selected, enemies inflicted with [Dark Corrosion] cannot receive positive effects, and have their Mana reduced by 250 every 1 sec.

name: Say Hello to Death!!
description: Sticks [Darkslayer Demonic Sword, Veil] into the ground, creating a shockwave that deals 332027 M.DMG to nearby enemies in a circular range of self and inflicts Stun for 5 sec. Afterward, for 10 sec, unloads [Dark Thunder] to a random enemy every 2 sec, dealing 58827 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 0.5 sec. If Darkslayer Demonic Sword, [Veil] is selected, the Mana Cost of all Skills increases by 1, but DMG inflicted by this Skill will ignore DEF and the Heal Rate of enemies hit by [Dark Thunder] will be reduced by 50% for 5 sec.

name: Three Demonic Swords
description: At the beginning of the first Battle, Kibera can select a demonic sword. He gains immunity to CC until he selects his sword, but he cannot recover mana during that period. Once he selects a sword, his stats and the effect of a skill will be enhanced depending on the selected sword. Nocturnal Demonic Sword, [Night Sky] - Increases ATK Spd by 300 and enhances the effect of [Mm, You Better Pay Attention]. Umbral Demonic Blade, [Dark Shadow] - Increases DEF by 18992 and enhances the effect of [Heh, Let's Have Some Fun!] and [Ha! Full of Openings]. Darkslayer Demonic Sword, [Veil] - Increases ATK by 28496 and enhances the effect of [Say Hello to Death!!].

name: Slash, Blade of Judgment!
description: Deals a total of 127673 M.DMG over 7 attacks to nearby enemies in a circular range of self. Then, attacks frontal enemies in range, dealing 189305 M.DMG and knocking them down for 3 sec.

name: Disperse, Crystal Haze!
description: Unleashes the power of Arcane Crystals within to deal 93166 M.DMG to all enemies and stun them for 2 sec. Upon casting, activates [Arcane Crystal Awakening] for 15 sec, which increases ATK Spd of all allies by 300 and releases a shockwave every 2 sec to enemies in range of self, dealing 102251 M.DMG and stunning them for 1 sec.

name: Bloom, Crimson Flower!
description: Summons Arcane Crystals and deals 172779 M.DMG to frontal enemies in a straight line. Shortly afterward, causes an explosion that deals 276243 additional M.DMG and inflicts [Arcane Crystal Curse] upon enemies for 5 sec, reducing their ATK Spd by 200. Attacking enemies under [Arcane Crystal Curse] inflicts a stack of [Arcane Crystal Energy]. [Arcane Crystal Curse] explodes after 5 sec, dealing M.DMG equal to 113842 + 9669 per stack of [Arcane Crystal Energy].

name: End to Evil Deeds!
description: Increases own ATK by 75992 and Crit Chance by 200, while increasing the duration of CCs that all allies inflict to Bosses by 30%.

name: Healing Droplets
description: Heals HP of all allies by 275339 and reduces M.DMG they take by 15% for 5 sec. If the target's HP is below 50%, Heal Rate and the amount of reduced M.DMG the target takes increases by x 1.5.

name: Bubble Shield
description: For 15 sec, casts a shield that blocks 989666 DMG on the ally with the lowest HP. While the shield is in effect, it grants Immunity to CC, increases the ATK by 35622 , and heals 39592 HP every sec for the ally.

name: Festival of the Flow
description: Deals 236352 M.DMG to nearby enemies and knocks them down. All allies, excluding self, recovers 2 orbs of mana. Afterwards, for 12 sec, creates a whirlpool that deals 157578 M.DMG to random enemies and knocks them down for 2 sec.

name: Blessing of the Water Dragon
description: All allies' M.DEF is increased by 4748 , and M.Crit Hit Resistance is increased by 250.

name: Rapid Fire
description: Attacks all frontal enemies in a straight line, dealing 265827 P.DMG and inflicting Stun for 3 sec. If the target is not a Hero, deals 127628 additional P.DMG. [Experiment Success!] Removes Cooldown.

name: Smoke Bomb
description: Deals 159466 P.DMG to target and nearby enemies within range and inflicts them with [Explosive Material] for 10 sec, causing them to take 20% increased P.DMG and additionally inflicting Blind for 4 sec. [Experiment Success!] Dispels positive effects from enemies within range.

name: Glue Bomb
description: Attaches a Glue Bomb to a random enemy that explodes in 3 sec to a random enemy, dealing 548169 P.DMG to the target and nearby enemies and inflicting Stun for 3 sec. If the target is inflicted with [Explosive Material], deals 359082 additional P.DMG. [Experiment Success!] Glue Bomb explodes immediately after attachment.

name: Load Cannon
description: Normal attacks have a 15% chance of firing a bomb that deals 124195 P.DMG to enemies within range and inflicting Stun for 2 sec. After each Skill use, Lakrak conducts and experiment. The experiment has a 50% success rate. Upon success, enhances the effects of the next skill use. Experiment does not occur when Lakrak uses the enhanced Skill.

name: Whisper of Sand
description: Attacks target enemy and deals 95775 M.DMG to enemies in close range, decreasing enemy block chance by 500 and Crit resistance by 500 for 8 sec. Additionally, attacks and deals 124518 M.DMG and stuns them for 3 sec.

name: Enchanting Flow
description: Increases own ATK by 28496 and Crit DMG by 70% for 10 sec. Then moves a short distance forward, dealing 898838 M.DMG to enemies in movement range and Charms them for 5 sec if the skill was used in the Arena. Can activate [Alluring Ambush] once within 5 sec after use.

name: Alluring Ambush
description: Attacks target enemy 3 times, dealing a total of 282705 M.DMG. Deals extra 133038 M.DMG ignoring the target's DEF to Boss enemies and enemies inflicted by Charm.

name: Dance of the Desert
description: Attacks enemies in range 30 times, dealing a total of 634410 M.DMG. Additionally throws the 'Blades of Arlaq' at random enemies 30 times, dealing a total of 427500 M.DMG. Extra 1900 DMG is stacked every time the blade hits the same enemy. [Blinding Acceleration] can be used once during skill activation, and the 'Blades of Arlaq' prioritize targets inflicted by Charm.

name: Blinding Acceleration
description: Gains immunity to CC for 3 sec and ATK Spd is increased by 800.

name: Blessing of Oasis
description: Decreases CC duration inflicted on self by 30%. Upon using a skill, gains [Blessing of Oasis] for 20 sec, increasing own Penetration by 30 and DEF by 1896. [Blessing of Oasis] can be stacked up to max 10 times and cannot be dispelled.

name: G-go Away!
description: Deals 196114 M.DMG to the enemy and reduces its Crit Resistance by 300 for 10 sec. Hit enemies become affected by Lavril's Ectoplasm for 5 sec, taking 34728 M.DMG every 0.5 sec. Every time an enemy takes DMG from this skill, HP of all allies is healed by 5% of the DMG dealt.

name: Bear Up...!
description: Heals the HP of an ally with the highest ATK by 318500 and heals additional 34194 HP every 1 sec for 15 sec. Increases Crit DMG of the ally by 50% + 15% of Lavril's Crit DMG for 15 sec. [You Scare Me...!] becomes available for 5 sec after casting this skill.

name: You Scare Me...!
description: Deals 296540 M.DMG to the enemy and reduces its ATK Spd by 250 for 15 sec while increasing M.DMG it takes by 25%.

name: Leave Me Alone...!
description: Swirls a Spectral Tornado in a wide range to the front, dealing 73723 M.DMG every 0.5 sec for 5 sec. Each hit reduces ATK of hit enemies by 3% for 5 sec, and increases M.DMG they take by 3%. This effect can be stacked up to max 15 times.

name: Together Forever...
description: At the beginning of the first battle, forms a Soul Link with an ally with the highest ATK. This effect cannot be dispelled. The ally bound by Soul Link has their ATK increased by 32055 and recovers 100 Mana every second.

name: Rune of Frailty
description: Engraves a rune on the target, dealing up to 203012 P.DMG that ignores DEF based on missing HP and reducing their P.DEF by 50% for 8 sec.

name: Rune of Healing
description: Heals 236468 HP of all allies.

name: Rune of Silence
description: Deals 88006 P.DMG to all enemies, and dispels all positive effects. Inflicts Silences on target for 3 sec.

name: Rune of Protection
description: Every 10 sec, engraves a rune upon the ally with the lowest HP and recovers a total of 312440 HP for 10 sec.

name: Blood Orb
description: Deals 293762 M.DMG to target, increasing M.DMG the target takes 25% for 10 sec. Each stacks of Blood Curse, inflicted upon target increases DMG dealt by 1%. Upon use, consumes 10% of current HP.

name: Blood Zone
description: Deals 352394 M.DMG to the target and creates a Blood Zone that lasts for 10 sec around the target. Enemies within the Blood Zone take 25205 M.DMG every 0.5 sec, and have their M.DEF is reduced by 30%. Each stack of Blood Curse inflicted upon target increases DMG dealt by 1%. Upon use, consumes 20% of current HP.

name: Blood Banquet
description: Attacks frontal enemies in a straight line 3 times, dealing a total of 308775 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 3 sec. Each stack of Blood Curse inflicted upon target increases DMG dealt by 1% Upon use, consumes 10% of current HP.

name: Blood Dominator
description: When HP is 50% or above, ATK is increased by 35148 and DEF Penetration  by 250. Upon attack, inflicts target with Blood Curse, dealing a total of 12900 continuous M.DMG over time for 20 sec and recovering HP equal to 10% of DMG dealt by Blood Curse. Blood Curse can be stacked up to max 60 times, and it is irremovable.

name: Aqua Tempest
description: For 8 sec, summons Aqua Tempest to a random target and enemies in target's range and deals 19217 P.DMG every 0.5 sec. If the target is killed, Aqua Tempest is summoned to attack another random target for the remaining time.

name: Everlasting Oasis
description: When activated, turns into the Everlasting Oasis state for 15 sec. During the Everlasting Oasis state, mana recovery rate per sec is increased by 150% and ATK is increased by 79077. Additionally, all DEF is increased by 9737.

name: Celestial Cataract
description: Throws water drops 15 times to random enemies, dealing a total of 343290 P.DMG. Additionally, throws big water drops 5 times to target and other enemies in target's range, dealing 559125 P.DMG. Enemies hit by the big water drop are inflicted by Stun for 2 sec. Per each water drop thrown, 25 mana is consumed, and mana consumption rate is increased by 13. Stops use when mana becomes 0.

name: Aqua Purification
description: Mana Recovery upon attack is fixed, but increaeses own ATK by 41559, Crit Chance by 300, and Mana Recovery per sec to 120. Per 6 Mana Recovery per sec, ATK is increased by 1%.

name: Cut Ground
description: Deals 138175 P.DMG to frontal enemies within range and knocks them down for 4 sec, increasing P.Weakness of the affected targets by 25% for 10 sec.

name: Shrouding Creed
description: Removes negative effects from all allies. Casts a shield upon all allies that absorbs 354966 DMG for 5 second(s) and reduces all DMG to allies by 20% for 10 second(s). The shield grants immunity to CC while it lasts.

name: Knight's Creed
description: Hits frontal enemies within range 3 times. First 2 hits deal 115539 P.DMG and stun enemies for 1.5 second(s) while the last hit attacks enemies in wider range 2 times, dealing 273022 P.DMG in total. The last hit stuns enemies for 5 seconds and leaves [Mark of Creed] on the enemies, damaging them for 15 second(s). Targets with [Mark of Creed] take additional 107504 P.DMG from allies excluding caster. Additional DMG effect is activated only once every 0.5 second(s).

name: The Last Gatekeeper
description: Stacks [Endurance] every second. [Endurance] cannot be dispelled, and when stacked 20 times, deals 7900 P.DMG, ignoring DEF on nearby enemies and reduces ATK of affected enemies by 20% for 10 second(s). A successful block grants 1 additional [Endurance] stack. This effect is activated only once every 0.2 second(s).

name: Thornbush Forest
description: Attacks a random enemy and its nearby enemies 3 times, dealing a total of 372021 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 3 sec.

name: Seed of Belladonna
description: Creates a Seed of Belladonna around the target for 10 sec. The seed deals 138584 M.DMG to nearby enemies every 2 sec, increasing M.DMG the target takes by 30% and reducing Heal Rate by 30% for 5 sec.

name: Wrath of the Forest
description: Attacks enemies within a wide frontal range of self 6 times, dealign a total of 630588 M.DMG and knocking them down for 3 sec.

name: Poison
description: Normal and Skill attacks inflict Poison on a target, dealing a total of 410580 continuous M.DMG and reducing Heal Rate by 5% over 20 sec. Poison can be stacked up to max 5 times.

name: Path of Blessings
description: Heals 4 allies with the lowest HP by 350151 and targets take 20% reduced P.DMG for 7 sec.

name: Zone of Faith
description: Sets up the [Zone of Faith] at the own location for 6 sec. Increases ATK of allies in [Zone of Faith] by 64833 and dispels negative effects on them continuously. Heals allies in area by 61303 every second. Deals P.DMG of 102501 on enemies within [Zone of Faith] every second, and stuns them for 0.7 sec.

name: Stigmata
description: Increases P.Dodge of all allies by 250 and their ATK by 36803 for 15 sec. Effects will be dispelled when the self dies. Normal attacks deal additional P.DMG of 208424 to targets for 15 sec, and increases the P.DMG taken by target by 25% for 5 sec.

name: Holy Sacrifice
description: Casting Path of Blessings and Zone of Faith consumes 20% of self's current HP. Upon healing an ally with these spells, the amount of healing is increased by 48947 and the target gains 4507 additional DEF for 10 sec.

name: Pew!
description: Deals 163643 M.DMG by shooting a bouncing projectile which bounces 3 times starting from the nearest enemy. The further the enemy, the more DMG inflicted.

name: Look out above!
description: Deals 284915 M.DMG to enemies furthest away in a small range, and stuns them for 3 sec. The further the enemy, the more DMG they will take.

name: Twinkle Twinkle
description: Deals 118336 M.DMG to target enemies in range, and reduces target's Crit Chance by 100% for 7 sec.

name: Gotcha!
description: When inflicted by CC, dispels negative effects from self and attacks the farthest enemy, dealing 38284 M.DMG and knocking it away for 2 sec. Affterward, recovers 1 orb of Mana.

name: Raven Storm
description: Deals a total of 481491 M.DMG over 3 times to enemies in frontal range and knocks them back, reducing hit enemies' ATK Spd by 250 and M.DEF by 30% for 15 sec. If the target is not a Hero, each hit deals 160497 additional M.DMG.

name: Claw of Restriction
description: Deals 218709 M.DMG to 2 enemies and shackles them for 6 sec. Hit targets take 63348 continuous M.DMG over 6 sec and take 30% increased M.DMG for the duration of Skill.

name: Area of Darkness
description: Draws in nearby enemies towards the center 5 times and deals a total of 607795 M.DMG. The last attack stuns enemies for 3 sec. Deals additional 121559 M.DMG to Non-Hero enemies.

name: Black Wind
description: Increases Crit Chance by 150 and each hit inflicts [Curse of Lea] on the target for 10 sec. Targets inflictes with [Curse of Lea] have theirCrit Chance reduced by 250 and ATK by 25% for the duration of Skill.

name: Take anything!
description: All allies' ATK is increased by 5222 for 120 sec, and randomly grants one of the following effects: 1. DEF Penetration 70 up, 2. Atk Spd 100 up, 3. Instant Mana recovery by 500. All effects other than Mana Recovery can be stacked up to 5 times max.

name: Cheer up!
description: All allies' HP is healed by 330736 , and per each sec, each ally recovers 1% of their max HP for 10 sec. There is a 10% chance the heal rate doubles.

name: Not for sale!
description: Attacks a random target and other enemies in range 3 times, dealing a total of 465795 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 4 sec. There is a 10% chance that the skill range, DMG, and Stun duration are doubled.

name: Take this!
description: Every 15 sec, deals 154304 M.DMG to 4 random enemies, and randomly inflicts one of the following: 1. 185720 M.DMG over time for 10 sec, 2. Stun for 2 sec, 3. Freeze for 5 sec

name: Healing Salve

description: With every attack, injects Electricity to targets not inflicted by Shock and increases M.DMG taken by 1% for 10 sec. Electricity can be stacked up to 30 times, and the 30th stack will consume all Electricity to deal 334703 M.DMG and Shock the target for 7 sec. Enemies inflicted by Shock take 70% increased M.DMG, and when they are inflicted by Stun, the duration is increased by 0.7 sec.

name: BOOM! Here Goes!
description: Attacks frontal enemies in a straight line, dealing 94601 P.DMG, inflicting Stun for 2 sec, and reducing All Block Chance by 350 for 8 sec. Afterward, deals 127849 P.DMG to enemies within range and knocks them down for 3 sec.

name: Protection! Was dat Lucky Stone?
description: Dispels negative effects from self, and while charging energy, Taily takes 50% reduced DMG. When fully charged, increases own Heal Rate by 25% and All DEF by 52244 for 10 sec. If this Skill is activated with 50 or more [Emblem of Courage] stacks, applies the effect to all allies and consumes all of the [Emblem of Courage] stacks.

name: Charge! Knight Commander Power!
description: Deals 296040 P.DMG over 5 times to nearby enemies in a circular range of self and gains [Power of da Shuti Tribe] stacks. Afterward, gathers strength and delivers a final blow, dealing 254252 P.DMG and increases All DMG the target takes by 30%+[2% per stack of Power of da Shuti Tribe] for 10 sec, and inflicts Stun for 3 sec. [Power of da Shuti Tribe] can be stacked up to max 30 times.

name: Blessing of da Shuti Tribe!
description: When HP percentage is 30% or above, attacks nearby enemies in range every sec, dealing 115769 P.DMG. Taily gains an irremovable stack of [Emblem of Courage] each hit. Each stack of [[Emblem of Courage] increases All DEF of all allies by 707. [Emblem of Courage] can be stacked up to max 50 times. When HP percentage is 30% or below, increases own All Block Chance by 700.

name: Target Sighted
description: Increases P.DMG the enemy with the lowest P.DEF takes by 30% for 10 sec, and moves behind the target, dealing 167461 P.DMG and knocking it down for 2 sec. If used during Stealth, 150% increased Crit DMG applies, and Stealth is dispelled. If Skill is used while not in Stealth, becomes Stealth for 10 sec.

name: Blade Tornado
description: Attacks nearby enemies 3 times and deals a total of 333339 P.DMG, inflicting 1 stack of Bleed per each hit. If used in a Stealth state, target's heal rate is reduced by 70%, and Stealth is dispelled. If Skill is used while not in Stealth, becomes Stealth for 10 sec.

name: Whisper of Death
description: Attacks a random enemy 6 times and deals a total of 947466 P.DMG, then deals an extra that deals 297146 P.DMG. If used during Stealth, dispels positive effects from the Target, and Stealth is dispelled. If Skill is used while not in Stealth, becomes Stealth for 10 sec.

name: Silent Ambush
description: Increases Crit Chance by 300 and Dodge by 300 during Stealth. Upon a Critical Skill Hit, deals 69004 additional P.DMG to the enemy and inflicts Silence for 2 sec. If the target is not a Hero, deals 48199 additional P.DMG that ignores DEF and reduces the target's ATK Spd by 200 for 10 sec.

name: Final Crash
description: Attacks 16 times, dealing a total of 361408 M.DMG to enemies in range. Upon each Crit Hit, Crit DMG is increased by 3% for 10 sec, and there is a 30% chance to deal 23776 extra M.DMG, inflicting stun for 0.3 sec. Crit DMG boost can be stacked up to 30 times max.

name: God of Lightning
description: Upon casting, activates 'God of Lightning' and throws a spear of lightning at the enemy, dealing 221647 M.DMG. Hit enemy takes 50% increased M.DMG for 10 sec. While in 'God of Lightning' state, increases activation chance of 'For Jane' is increased by 40% and ATK is increased by 71244 for 15 sec.

name: Lightning Explosion
description: Jumps and strikes, thrusting the spear to the ground and hitting target enemy and enemies in range 5 times, dealing a total of 346445 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 3 sec.

name: For Jane
description: Each auto attack has a 20% chance of dealing 122422 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 0.7 sec.

name: This will hurt a little!
description: Deals 215290 M.DMG to enemy and surrounding enemies within range, and inflicts Stun for 2 sec.

name: Let me help you.
description: Grants a Rune to all allies to increase their ATK by 56992 and any DMG to bosses by 15% for 12 sec.

name: Get out of my sight!
description: Attacks target and enemies in a wide surrounding area 2 times to deal 392862 M.DMG, and knocks them down for 5 sec. Hit enemies take 30% increased M.DMG for 10 sec.

name: Top Financier's Knowledge
description: Increases ATK of all allies by 5696 and gains Experience stack upon using a Skill. When 3 Experiences are stacked, gains Top Financier's Knowledge that increases own Crit DMG by 30% and the effects of all active Skills by 10%. The Top Financier's Knowledge effect is irremovable and stacks up to 5 times.

name: Meal Time!!
description: Deals 217775 M.DMG to frontal enemies in range. For 10 sec, Hit enemies' ATK is reduced by 25% for and own ATK is increased by 42740. If used while holding 3 or more stacks of Soul, shackles the enemy for 3 sec.

name: I'll slice you up!!
description: Moves behind the target, dispelling positive effects and dealing 184564 M.DMG, increases M.DMG the target takes by 25% for 15 sec, and knock it down. If used while holding 3 or more stacks of Soul, reduces enemy M.DEF by 30% for 15 sec.

name: I'll rip you to pieces!!
description: Deals 343869 M.DMG to enemies in a wide surrounding area, and inflicts Stun for 3 sec. If used while holding 5 stacks of Soul, consumes all stacks to reset the cooldown of this skill.

name: Yummy Souls!
description: Enemies attacked with Viska's skills lose Souls. Upon losing their Soul, targets take 32032 extra M.DMG, and per each soul stacked, Viska's HP is healed by 63853 and Mana is healed by 300. Souls last until they are used, can't be dispelled and can be stacked up to 5 times max.

name: Orbs of Darkness
description: Throws 6 orbs of darkness, dealing a total of 350658 M.DMG to a random enemy and enemies in a circular range of the target. When Xerah is in [Darkness Awakened] state, increases DMG of [Orbs of Darkness] by x2, and reduces Cooldown by 100%. [Crest of Extortion Level 1 Effect] Destroys shield from the target.

name: Crest of Extortion
description: Dispels negative effects from self and casts Crest of Extortion that lasts permanently on self. If Xerah already possesses a Crest of Extortion, the level of Crest of Extortion increases instead. [Crest of Extortion] Deals 189967 M.DMG to a random enemy every 5 sec. Level 1: Adds an additional effect to [Orbs of Darkness] Skill. Level 2: Effect activation interval changes to 4 sec, and adds an additional effect to [Blood Moon] Skill. Level 3: Effect activation interval changes to 3 sec, and [Crest of Extortion] Skill changes to [Crest Bestowal] Skill.

name: Crest Bestowal
description: Upon use, dispels negative effects from self and bestows the power of the Crest of Extortion to an ally with the lowest HP. The ally instantly recovers 1 orb of Mana, heals its HP by a total of 515420 for 5 sec, and gains Immunity to CC.

name: Blood Moon
description: Creates a [Blood Moon] for 10 sec. For the duration of Blood Moon, increases ATK of all allies by 80740, reduces DMG taken by 20%, deals a total of 850510 M.DMG to all enemies, and reduces their Heal Rate by 50%. [Crest of Extortion Level 2 Effect] Boosts the effect all allies receive by x2.

name: Darkness Awakened
description: Upon using a Skill, if Xerah is not in Darkness Awakened state, gains an irremovable stack of [Darkness]. Upon gaining 4 [Darkness] stacks, Xerah consumes the stacks to enter [Darkness Awakened] state that is irremovable for 10 sec, increasing Lifesteal by 200 and dealing 50% increased DMG to Non-Hero enemies. When Xerah takes fatal DMG while in [Darkness Awakened] state, [Darkness Awakened] becomes deactivated, consumes entire Mana of self, and heals HP by 30%. Afterward, Xerah cannot gain any Darkness stacks for 10 sec.

name: Focus Shot!
description: Taking up a stance, focuses for a while and deals 226461 P.DMG to enemies in a straight line. If the target is a dragon, inflicts Stun for 3 sec. The longer she focuses, DMG and Stun duration are increased by 100%.

name: Wipeout!
description: Deals 314476 P.DMG to target enemy and other enemies in range. If the target is a Dragon, deals 250496 extra DMG that ignores DEF.

name: No Holding Back!
description: Dispels all negative effects from self. For 30 sec, ATK is increased by 36096 and Penetration by 500. For the duration of skill, normal attacks consume 3% Mana to deal DMG to all enemies in a straight line and deals 41796 additional P.DMG that ignores DEF to Dragons. This effect is irremovable.

name: Dragon Slayer
description: ATK is increased by 10685 , and Max HP is increased by 30%. Also, DMG dealt to Dragons is increased by 100%.

name: Binding Karma

name: Circle of Fate

Enemies under 'Threading Destiny' have their ATK Spd reduced by 250. If the target is not a Hero, deals 212256 additional M.DMG.

name: Blessing of Truth
description: Increases own All DEF by 9737 and ATK Spd by 300. Normal attacks hit 2 enemies. Every normal attack inflicts a stack of 'Stigma of Stars' upon enemies. Targets take 1% increased M.DMG for every stack of 'Stigma of Stars'. This effect can be stacked up to max 15 times and is irremovable.

name: Judgment of the Desert
description: Deals 182140 P.DMG to enemies in a wide range, and per each enemies hit, reduces Cooldown by 1 sec. Deals 364309 P.DMG to enemies inflicted by [Mark of Desert] and removes 1 stack of [Mark of Desert]. Upon each Skill use, Crit DMG is increased by 5%. This effect can be stacked up to max 18 times and is irremovable.

name: Blessing of the Sand Spirit
description: Creates a shield around the ally with the lowest HP that absorbs 534273 DMG for 5 sec. Gains immunity to CC while the shield lasts. When the shield duration is over, 'Sand Storm' is activated and deals 261124 P.DMG to enemies in a wide range, inflicting 2 stacks of [Mark of Desert]. If the shield is dispelled or destroyed, 'Sand Storm' does not activate.

name: Doom of the Desert
description: Deals 123855 P.DMG to frontal enemies in a wide range and inflicts 1 stack of [Mark of Desert]. Then summons 'Pit of Sand' for 5 sec, dealing 41350 P.DMG every 0.5 sec, and decreasing their P.DEF by 30% for 10 sec. 'Pit of Sand' has a 25% chance of inflicting 1 stack of [Mark of Desert] and draws in all enemies in range to the center.

name: Calling of the Guardian
description: Each auto attack has a 15% chance of dealing 96597 P.DMG that ignores DEF to all enemies, inflicting 1 stack of [Mark of Desert]. [Mark of Desert] can be stacked up to max 10 times.

name: Radiance of Cimatis
description: Deals 262231 M.DMG to the target and neartby enemies. Upon attacking the same target with this skill within 7 sec, deals 239939 additional M.DMG that ignores DEF. Cooldown will be applied every time this Skill is used 2 times.

name: Dance of Luberry
description: Attacks the target and nearby enemies within a small range 9 times, dealing a total of 388116 M.DMG and inflicting Stun on the target for 1 sec each hit. If the target is a boss, the last hit deals 172346 additional M.DMG that ignores DEF.

name: Splendor of Cimatis
description: Explodes Cimatis around the target, dealing 193125 M.DMG and creating [Splendor of Cimatis] for 10 sec. [Splendor of Cimatis] recovers Mana of allies within range by 400 every sec and deals 30703 M.DMG to enemies within range every sec.

name: Full Bloom of Luberry
description: Explodes Luberry in front of self, healing HP of allies within range by 147415 and creating [Full Bloom of Luberry] for 10 sec. [Full Bloom of Luberry] heals HP of all allies within range by 25825 every sec and reduces ATK of Enemies within range by 30%.

name: Crystal of Resonance
description: Talisha projects Light of Luberry to the crystal she owns, healing own HP by 101047 and changes [Radicance of Cimatis] and [Splendor of Cimatis] to [Dance of Luberry] and [Full Bloom of Luberry] respectively. Upon using this Skill again, Talisha projects Light of Cimatis to the crystal and recovers Mana by 500.

name: Brilliant Gemologist
description: Talisha appraises a gem, increasing ATK by 6170 and DMG dealt to non-Hero enemies by 1% every sec. This effect can be stacked up to max 30 times.

name: Void Whirlwind
description: Deals a total of 302832 M.DMG over 12 hits to frontal enemies. Each hit reduces the targets Mana by 150.

name: Transcendant

Hilda also reduces Heal Rate of nearby enemies within circular range by 30%, and consumes own mana by 100 every sec. The mana consumption gradually increases over time, and [Transcendant] state deactivates upon consuming all Mana or using a Skill.

name: Void Strike
description: Deals 332668 M.DMG to frontal enemies within circular range of self and knocks them down for 3 sec. Upon hitting an enemy inflicted with [Void], consumes all Void stacks from the target and deals 13762 additional M.DMG per stack

Upon dealing DMG to an enemy inflicted with [Ignite], the Skill changes to [Blazing Storm], dealing 80853 P.DMG and reducing enemy’s Heal Rate by 1.5% for 60 sec each hit. This effect can be stacked up to max 30 times.

name: Quintessence of Technomagic
description: Isolet’s ATK Spd is fixed to 1000 and she is not affected by Skill Cooldown Reduction effects, by she recovers 1500 Mana and increases her Crit DMG by 100% every time she uses a Skill. When she creates [Blazing Storm], M.DMG all allies take is reduced by 7%. This effect can be stacked up to max 3 times and is irremovable.

name: Determined Strike
description: Deals 131671 P.DMG to frontal enmemies within range and inflicts Stun for 2 sec. If the target is a boss, deals 305302 additional P.DMG.

name: Indomitable Will
description: Deals 49114 P.DMG to nearby enemies, entering into the irremoveable state [Indomitable Will] for 10 sec. While in [Indomitable Will] state, ATK Spd is increased by 500 and the duration of CC inflicted upon self is reduced by 50%.

name: Perish

Additionally, his normal attack deal 92895 additional P.DMG to all enemies and inflict [Curse of Galicta] upon them for 6 sec. If the target is already inflicted with [Curse of Galicta], the target won't take additional DMG.

Attacks an enemy 5 times, dealing 88995 M.DMG and inflicting [Pochi's Mark] each hit. The M.DMG of each hit increases by 15% per every stack of [Mana Charge]. The additional M.DMG increases by 30% per every stack of [Mana Charge].
This skill is sealed after use.

Attacks the farthest enemy from behind, inflicting [Puchi's Mark] on the target, dealing 225218 M.DMG and inflicting Stun for 5 sec. [Puchi's Mark] reduces the target's M.Block Chance by 500 for 12 sec.
This Skill is sealed after use.

description: Attacks the target 5 times, dealing a total of 348575 M.DMG and delivers an additional attack that deals 264048 M.DMG. The last hit deals 6172 additional M.DMG that ignores DEF per stack of [Otherworldly Curse].
